description:
Box Swap game is highly addictive. You will not be able to put this game down ;-) Hours of fun!
WARNING: The game is not easy! But you have possibility to find out level solutions online!

It will help to train your problem solving skills.
This logic game is all about moving boxes. You have to put in line three or more boxes and they will disappear.
You have to make them all disappear in limited number of moves!

This is free version with 100 levels.
Full version has 1000 levels.

FEATURES:
* Online solution check (requires internet connection)
* Adorable graphics
* Turn on/off sound effects
* Fun for the whole family!
